        <item>
            <title>年节家宴DIY~~吉祥四喜煲~~</title>
            <link>http://blog.sina.com.cn/s/blog_4df516880102dwrw.html</link>
            <description><![CDATA[<p><span STYLE="FonT-FAMiLY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin">
&nbsp;&nbsp;
&nbsp;要过年喽</SPAN><span LANG="EN-US">~~</SPAN><span STYLE="FonT-FAMiLY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin">张灯结彩贴春联</SPAN><span LANG="EN-US">~~</SPAN><span STYLE="FonT-FAMiLY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin">各位博友，龙年大吉，平安如意，恭喜发财哦</SPAN><span LANG="EN-US">~~~</SPAN><img SRC="http://www.sinaimg.cn/uc/myshow/blog/misc/gif/E___6724EN00SIGG.gif" TYPE="face" /></P>
<p><span STYLE="FonT-FAMiLY: 宋体"><br /></SPAN></P>
<p>&nbsp;&nbsp;
&nbsp;<span STYLE="FonT-FAMiLY: 宋体">兔年最后一博，一定要拿出看家本事，不怕献丑，做一道喜庆家宴给大家吃吃。呵呵。</SPAN><img SRC="http://www.sinaimg.cn/uc/myshow/blog/misc/gif/E___6717EN00SIGG.gif" TYPE="face" /></P>
<p><span LANG="EN-US">&nbsp;</SPAN></P>
<p><span STYLE="FonT-FAMiLY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin">
&nbsp;&nbsp;
&nbsp;话说当年，嗯，就是我们小时候啊，过春节真是大事件，有新衣服穿，有好东西吃，尤其年夜饭，那个丰盛啊。真令人向往。现在生活富裕了，吃的东东貌似有无限选择，只要你愿意，天天能过节。所以，春节吃什么，都不算啥事儿了。而且工作这么忙，好容易放假了，年夜饭很多人都选择出去吃，或者叫外卖到家里。自己做饭的越来越少了。</SPAN><img SRC="http://www.sinaimg.cn/uc/myshow/blog/misc/gif/E___6711EN00SIGG.gif" TYPE="face" /></P>
<p><span LANG="EN-US">&nbsp;</SPAN></P>
<span STYLE="FonT-siZe: 10.5pt; FonT-FAMiLY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-bidi-font-size: 11.0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 'Times new roman'; mso-bidi-theme-font: minor-bidi; mso-ansi-language: en-Us; mso-fareast-language: ZH-Cn; mso-bidi-language: Ar-sA">&nbsp;&nbsp;
&nbsp;上回说了，今年春节我准备宅在家里，好好陪长辈过节。这样的话，年夜饭就要很精心准备喽。各种美食，各种小吃，早早的我们就开始筹备了。很有气氛滴说。小车我从小离家，拍戏也是东奔西走，厨艺涅，还好吧，不算很精，拿手菜还是有一些滴。在这里献上一道吧，吉祥四喜煲，很简单，很营养，很好彩。口味不油腻，也挺适合大鱼大肉的年节时刻滴。</SPAN><img SRC="http://www.sinaimg.cn/uc/myshow/blog/misc/gif/E___6725EN00SIGG.gif" TYPE="face" />
<div><br /></DIV>
<div><a HREF="http://blog.photo.sina.com.cn/showpic.html#url=http://s9.sinaimg.cn/orignal/4df51688tb6b45130e0e8" TARGET="_blank"><img SRC="http://s9.sinaimg.cn/middle/4df51688tb6b45130e0e8&amp;690" /></A><br />

<br />
&nbsp;<span STYLE="FonT-FAMiLY: 宋体">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
这道菜的原材料主要包括：乌鸡，竹荪，冬瓜，香菇；</SPAN><span STYLE="FonT-FAMiLY: 宋体">配料有：枸杞，金华火腿；</SPAN><span STYLE="FonT-FAMiLY: 宋体">调料有：盐，鸡粉或鸡精，葱，姜，香菜。</SPAN></DIV>
<div>
<div>
<p STYLE="FonT-FAMiLY: 宋体"><span LANG="EN-US">&nbsp;
<a HREF="http://blog.photo.sina.com.cn/showpic.html#url=http://s15.sinaimg.cn/orignal/4df51688tb6b40b08719e" TARGET="_blank"><img STYLE="WiDTH: 318px; HeiGHT: 211px" HEIGHT="460" SRC="http://s15.sinaimg.cn/middle/4df51688tb6b40b08719e&amp;690" WIDTH="690" /></A>&nbsp; <a HREF="http://blog.photo.sina.com.cn/showpic.html#url=http://s11.sinaimg.cn/orignal/4df51688tb6b40b68634a" TARGET="_blank"><img STYLE="WiDTH: 324px; HeiGHT: 214px" HEIGHT="460" SRC="http://s11.sinaimg.cn/middle/4df51688tb6b40b68634a&amp;690" WIDTH="690" /></A><br />
&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
乌鸡&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
冬瓜<br />
&nbsp; <a HREF="http://blog.photo.sina.com.cn/showpic.html#url=http://s3.sinaimg.cn/orignal/4df51688tb6b40bd1a1c2" TARGET="_blank"><img STYLE="WiDTH: 318px; HeiGHT: 213px" HEIGHT="460" SRC="http://s3.sinaimg.cn/middle/4df51688tb6b40bd1a1c2&amp;690" WIDTH="690" /></A>&nbsp; <a HREF="http://blog.photo.sina.com.cn/showpic.html#url=http://s5.sinaimg.cn/orignal/4df51688tb6b40c5aab74" TARGET="_blank"><img STYLE="WiDTH: 325px; HeiGHT: 215px" HEIGHT="460" SRC="http://s5.sinaimg.cn/middle/4df51688tb6b40c5aab74&amp;690" WIDTH="690" /></A><br />
&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;香菇&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
&nbsp;&nbsp; 竹荪<br />
<a HREF="http://blog.photo.sina.com.cn/showpic.html#url=http://s13.sinaimg.cn/orignal/4df51688tb6b40cd4f6dc" TARGET="_blank"></A><br /></SPAN></P>
<p STYLE="FonT-FAMiLY: 宋体"><span LANG="EN-US">&nbsp;</SPAN><span STYLE="FonT-FAMiLY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;做法呢，非常简单。当然啦，如果复杂滴话，我还真不一定搞得定耶。</SPAN></P>
<p STYLE="FonT-FAMiLY: 宋体"><span LANG="EN-US">&nbsp;</SPAN></P>
<p STYLE="FonT-FAMiLY: 宋体"><span STYLE="FonT-FAMiLY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin">
&nbsp;&nbsp;
&nbsp;第一步：先将乌鸡剁成块儿，注意，不要块儿太小，否则煲汤时肉就“烂”了，不美观也不好吃。冬瓜切块儿。竹荪、香菇如果买的是干的，要用温水泡发后切成段儿和块儿。葱切段。姜切片。</SPAN></P>
<p STYLE="FonT-FAMiLY: 宋体"><span STYLE="FonT-FAMiLY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin">
&nbsp;&nbsp;
&nbsp;第二步：做一锅水，将乌鸡焯一下，水开后撇去浮沫。</SPAN></P>
<p STYLE="FonT-FAMiLY: 宋体"><span STYLE="FonT-FAMiLY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin">
&nbsp;&nbsp;
&nbsp;第三步：另做一锅清水，将焯过的乌鸡、香菇、枸杞以及盐、鸡粉、葱、姜等一起放入锅中，中火炖</SPAN><span LANG="EN-US">10-20</SPAN><span STYLE="FonT-FAMiLY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin">分钟。</SPAN></P>
<p STYLE="FonT-FAMiLY: 宋体"><span STYLE="FonT-FAMiLY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin">
&nbsp;&nbsp;
&nbsp;第四步：在放入冬瓜、竹荪、火腿（这几样容易熟，放早了就“烂”了），再继续炖</SPAN><span LANG="EN-US">20</SPAN><span STYLE="FonT-FAMiLY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin">分钟左右就好喽。上桌前将香菜摆在汤上，摆个造型哈。</SPAN></P>
<p STYLE="FonT-FAMiLY: 宋体"><span LANG="EN-US">&nbsp;<a HREF="http://blog.photo.sina.com.cn/showpic.html#url=http://s13.sinaimg.cn/orignal/4df51688tb6b40cd4f6dc" TARGET="_blank"><img SRC="http://s13.sinaimg.cn/middle/4df51688tb6b40cd4f6dc&amp;690" /></A></SPAN></P>
<p STYLE="FonT-FAMiLY: 宋体">&nbsp;</P>
<p STYLE="FonT-FAMiLY: 宋体"><span LANG="EN-US">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
怎么样？我的手艺还好吧？这道菜材料很容易准备，制作简单，营养丰富，口味清淡，我挺喜欢滴。各位博友，您要不要试试看？</SPAN></P>
<p STYLE="FonT-FAMiLY: 宋体">&nbsp;</P>
</DIV>
</DIV>]]></description>
